id og ressurser p\u00e5 dette, mener Johansen Perreau.", "F\u00f8lg Adresseavisen p\u00e5 Facebook , Instagram og Twitter ."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "e4bc0ae1d734f888e07cc375fc5f5e6f2ffbdcb04411c43af0e0eb548e72c35e"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-03-16T21:39:41.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Ut\u00f8ya-etterlatte Randi og Sebastian Johansen Perreau har ingen tro p\u00e5 at Breivik vil si unnskyld til AUF og Arbeiderpartiet."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/nyheter/article12278861.ece/ilyajo/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Sebastian%20Perreau%204141.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/128595d57385f48cfb59f855238b8f48748e2d45.jpg?5974617f"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Breivik gj\u00f8r dette for \u00e5 provosere -adressa.no", "- Vanskelig \u00e5 h\u00f8re p\u00e5", "- Ville si unnskyld", "- Kan ikke slippe ut", "- Ingen vanlig fange"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "128595d57385f48cfb59f855238b8f48748e2d45"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Skien fengsel", "Oslo tingrett", "Breivik-rettssaken", "2207"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Skien fengsel,Oslo tingrett,Breivik-rettssaken,2207"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": ["sports", "law-government-and-politics"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["fengsel", "vanlig fange", "dag", "rettsstatens prinsipper", "unnskyld"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["randi og sebastian johansen perreau", "adresseavisen", "arbeiderpartiet", "johansen perreau"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["trondheim", "oslo", "hommelvik", "skien"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-perso